EMAIL.Subject: FW from AIM Server: Message from Barry Unger
EMAIL.Message: Hello. This is an electronically mailed display message from Barry Unger in response to your response to my telephone response mechanism. ± ± I have currently returned and am now available on the world wide web location site of AIM if you are still interested in the services I provide. ± ± Thank you. ±
